com.rockhoppertech.music.midi.js

Class MIDIEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rockhoppertech.music.midi.js.MIDIEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<MIDIEvent>

    public class MIDIEvent
extends Object
implements Serializable, Comparable<MIDIEvent>
    Class MIDIEvent wraps and adds to Java Sound's MidiEvent class. Sun's MidiEvent class is not Serializable. It is also useful to schedule events at beats instead of ticks.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Gene De Lisa
    See Also:
    Serializable, Serialized Form
